perl-test-exception: perl-test-exception (Test functions for exception based Perl code)
perl-test-exception:
perl-test-exception: This module provides a few convenience methods for testing exception
perl-test-exception: based code. It is built with Test::Builder and plays happily with
perl-test-exception: Test::More and friends.
